    {
      "name": "5. アフィリエイト連携",
      "description": "affiliateId を付けるとレスポンスに `affiliateUrl` / `affiliateRate` / `shopAffiliateUrl` が追加される。",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "affiliateId 付きで検索",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{BASE_URL}}/IchibaItem/Search/20260401?applicationId={{APPLICATION_ID}}&affiliateId={{AFFILIATE_ID}}&keyword=ふるさと納税 牡蠣&hits=5&format=json&field=0",
              "host": ["{{BASE_URL}}"],
              "path": ["IchibaItem", "Search", "20260401"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "applicationId", "value": "{{APPLICATION_ID}}" },
                { "key": "affiliateId", "value": "{{AFFILIATE_ID}}" },
                { "key": "keyword", "value": "ふるさと納税 牡蠣" },
                { "key": "hits", "value": "5" },
                { "key": "format", "value": "json" },
                { "key": "field", "value": "0" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "**確認ポイント**:\n- `Items[0].Item.affiliateUrl` が `https://hb.afl.rakuten.co.jp/...` 形式\n- `Items[0].Item.affiliateRate` に料率（%）が入る\n- `Items[0].Item.shopAffiliateUrl` も追加される（新仕様）"
          }
